'''Altan Telgey''' is a [[Mongol]] earth goddess. Her relationship to [[Etugen]] is unclear. In Mongolian, Delkhey (Delkhi) literally means earth. In modern Mongolian songs, the term Altan Delkhi is commonly mentioned.

